    {
      "text": " I run my restaurant only me alone, and no holidays",
      "start": 344.875,
      "duration": 5.25
    },
    {
      "text": "The way people interact with you is",
      "start": 378.166,
      "duration": 1.959
    },
    {
      "text": "going to be mostly based on",
      "start": 380.125,
      "duration": 1.166
    },
    {
      "text": "the way you interact with them",
      "start": 381.291,
      "duration": 1.209
    },
    {
      "text": "Now a lot of people wonder about the",
      "start": 383.958,
      "duration": 1.458
    },
    {
      "text": "social interactions in South Korea",
      "start": 385.416,
      "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
      "text": "And if people are standoffish or friendly",
      "start": 386.791,
      "duration": 3.709
    },
    {
      "text": "or something in between",
      "start": 390.5,
      "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
      "text": "And I think it really largely depends on",
      "start": 392.791,
      "duration": 2.375
    },
    {
      "text": "how you approach them",
      "start": 395.166,
      "duration": 0.959
    },
    {
      "text": "A lot of people are really just kind of",
      "start": 396.125,
      "duration": 2.416
    },
    {
      "text": "minding their own business",
      "start": 398.541,
      "duration": 0.917
    },
    {
      "text": "And if you don't speak to them, then they",
      "start": 399.791,
      "duration": 1.959
    },
    {
      "text": "might not think to speak to you first",
      "start": 401.75,
      "duration": 2.041
    },
    {
      "text": "But once you kind of break through that",
      "start": 403.791,
      "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
      "text": "barrier, I mean, these people will open",
      "start": 405.458,
      "duration": 2.375
    },
    {
      "text": "up their homes to you",
      "start": 407.833,
      "duration": 1.042
    },
    {
      "text": "The entire culture there is built on",
      "start": 409.125,
      "duration": 1.708
    },
    {
      "text": "respect and it's even",
      "start": 410.833,
      "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
      "text": "built into the language itself",
      "start": 412.5,
      "duration": 1.791
    },
    {
      "text": "I met up with a friend who has actually been living in ",
      "start": 416.375,
      "duration": 1.625
    },
    {
      "text": "South Korea for over 10 years",
      "start": 418.0,
      "duration": 1.791
    },
    {
      "text": "and we had a conversation about ",
      "start": 420.833,
      "duration": 1.292
    },
    {
      "text": "his experience living here",
      "start": 422.125,
      "duration": 1.541
    },
    {
      "text": "It's like even the other day, I was at a",
      "start": 424.5,
      "duration": 4.125
    },
    {
      "text": "bus stop and it was raining",
      "start": 428.625,
      "duration": 0.916
    },
    {
      "text": "And this really, really",
      "start": 429.541,
      "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
      "text": "old woman got off the bus",
      "start": 430.916,
      "duration": 1.834
    },
    {
      "text": "She didn't have an umbrella and she was",
      "start": 432.75,
      "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
      "text": "putting a plastic bag on her head",
      "start": 434.5,
      "duration": 1.541
    },
    {
      "text": "And then there was these",
      "start": 436.041,
      "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
      "text": "older ladies next to me",
      "start": 437.541,
      "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Who I would say were in their 60s, but",
      "start": 439.041,
      "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
      "text": "relatively much younger than this woman",
      "start": 440.791,
      "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
      "text": "It was probably like 80s or 90s, honestly",
      "start": 442.791,
      "duration": 3.084
    },
    {
      "text": "Wow",
      "start": 446.583,
      "duration": 0.542
    },
    {
      "text": "Didn't matter that her bus was coming,",
      "start": 447.5,
      "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
      "text": "she took her umbrella and walked the",
      "start": 449.75,
      "duration": 2.041
    },
    {
      "text": "woman to the subway station",
      "start": 451.791,
      "duration": 1.709
    },
    {
      "text": "Wow, went out of her way",
      "start": 453.5,
      "duration": 2.375
    },
    {
      "text": "That's what you gotta do",
      "start": 455.875,
      "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah\nSo that's part of Korean culture",
      "start": 456.833,
      "duration": 2.375
    },
    {
      "text": "And so Koreans actually have a word, I",
      "start": 459.5,
      "duration": 2.916
    },
    {
      "text": "forgot what it is, but",
      "start": 462.416,
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "there's a word for like",
      "start": 463.416,
      "duration": 1.459
    },
    {
      "text": "If somebody needs help, you have to go to",
      "start": 465.291,
      "duration": 1.917
    },
    {
      "text": "the extra mile to help them",
      "start": 467.208,
      "duration": 1.792
    },
    {
      "text": "Okay",
      "start": 469.166,
      "duration": 0.334
    },
    {
      "text": "So for example, if you ask somebody like,",
      "start": 469.5,
      "duration": 2.083
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Hey, I'm trying to get",
      "start": 471.583,
      "duration": 0.958
    },
    {
      "text": "to this subway station",
      "start": 472.541,
      "duration": 0.959
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you know where it is?\"",
      "start": 473.5,
      "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
      "text": "They won't just tell you",
      "start": 475.333,
      "duration": 0.792
    },
    {
      "text": "where it is, they'll take you",
      "start": 476.125,
      "duration": 1.041
    },
    {
      "text": "They'll take you to the... yeah",
      "start": 477.166,
      "duration": 1.084
    },
    {
      "text": "And so that happened to me too",
      "start": 478.5,
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Where it's like, \"Hey, I'm trying to get",
      "start": 479.5,
      "duration": 3.541
    },
    {
      "text": "to this subway station",
      "start": 483.041,
      "duration": 0.542
    },
    {
      "text": "Can you point me in the direction?\"",
      "start": 483.583,
      "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
      "text": "And they're like, \"Oh, come with me\"",
      "start": 485.0,
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah Doesn't matter what they're doing",
      "start": 486.375,
      "duration": 0.916
    },
    {
      "text": "But it's like a manners thing, like the",
      "start": 487.5,
      "duration": 3.291
    },
    {
      "text": "obligation they feel to help you",
      "start": 490.791,
      "duration": 2.334
    },
    {
      "text": "And not specifically towards foreigners,",
      "start": 493.166,
      "duration": 3.834
    },
    {
      "text": "just anybody who needs help with anything",
      "start": 497.458,
      "duration": 1.708
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh, absolutely",
      "start": 499.166,
      "duration": 0.542
    },
    {
      "text": "If you can help, then do it",
      "start": 499.708,
      "duration": 1.625
    },
    {
      "text": "I would say",
      "start": 501.625,
      "duration": 0.416
    },
    {
      "text": "particularly foreigners and elderly",
      "start": 502.041,
      "duration": 1.917
    },
    {
      "text": "So when it comes to nightlife in Seoul,",
      "start": 507.458,
      "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
      "text": "going out in this city is",
      "start": 509.416,
      "duration": 1.375
    },
    {
      "text": "not for the faint of heart",
      "start": 510.791,
      "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
      "text": "But it's such a good time",
      "start": 512.375,
      "duration": 1.041
    },
    {
      "text": "Koreans actually drink the most hard",
      "start": 513.75,
      "duration": 1.666
    },
